      "id": "project-5",
      "description": "Nawader Al Riyadh",
      "longDescription": "Nadira Riyadh Telecommunications Complex | Design & Build Executed by: Elc Contracting At Elc Contracting, we delivered a turnkey solution for the Nadira Riyadh Complex, transforming the space into a modern tech hub that balances high-impact branding with retail functionality. Project Scope & Highlights: Exterior Facade & Signage: We designed and installed a contemporary Cladding facade featuring high-visibility 3D backlit LED signage to ensure a dominant street presence. Custom Retail Counters: Our team manufactured and installed organized, numbered sales booths, each integrated with signature blue LED strip lighting to reinforce the brand identity. Premium Display Units: We equipped the showroom with custom glass showcases designed for maximum product visibility, security, and organized merchandising. Interior Infrastructure: The project included a complete lighting system and high-gloss flooring, creating a bright, professional, and spacious environment for customers.",
