      "id": "project-6",
      "description": "Alwaleed’s Private Office",
      "longDescription": "The Luxury of Simplicity: Office Design & Execution for the Private Office Manager of HRH Prince Alwaleed Bin TalalProject Description: Elc Contracting proudly presents this interior masterpiece. We undertook the complete design and execution of the office for the Private Office Manager of HRH Prince Alwaleed Bin Talal. Our vision for this project was to craft a workspace that embodies professional sophistication while ensuring maximum comfort and tranquillity. The project features refined modern touches, including: Flooring: The use of luxurious Grey Marble with natural veins creates a sense of spaciousness and grandeur. Lighting: A thoughtful distribution of ambient lighting and spotlights, complemented by concealed lighting in the ceiling and shelving units to accentuate the design aesthetics. Furniture & Woodwork: We selected a sleek, curved white desk to soften traditional lines, paired with a lounge area that combines modern sofas and comfortable seating for hosting guests. Walls & Decor: A harmonious blend of soft, light paint and dark wood cladding behind the display screen creates an elegant and attractive visual contrast.",
